## What are "Models"?

This license applies to:

- All `.pt` (PyTorch) model files in `data/models/`
- Pre-trained weights and parameters
- Model architecture definitions when distributed with weights

This license does NOT apply to:

- The source code (see [LICENSE](LICENSE) - Apache 2.0)
- Documentation and examples
- Training data (see Xeno-canto license terms)

