## Attribution Example

When using these models, please include attribution such as:

> "Vocalization classification models from EMSN 2.0 by Ronny Hullegie,
> licensed under CC BY-NC 4.0. https://github.com/ronnyhull/emsn2"

Or in academic work:

```bibtex
@software{emsn2_vocalization,
  author       = {Hullegie, Ronny},
  title        = {EMSN 2.0 Vocalization Classifier},
  year         = {2025},
  publisher    = {GitHub},
  url          = {https://github.com/ronnyhull/emsn2}
}
```

