## Training Data Attribution

The models were trained using audio recordings from [Xeno-canto](https://xeno-canto.org), a citizen science project for sharing bird sounds. Individual recordings may have different Creative Commons licenses. When using these models, please also acknowledge Xeno-canto's contribution to bird sound research.

